3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrude%20and%20gold%20initially%20jumped%20in%20early%20trading%20on%20Friday%2C%20but%20later%20pared%20their%20gains%20as%20reports%20suggested%20the%20apparent%20attack%20was%20far%20from%20extensive.%20A%20senior%20Iranian%20military%20official%20also%20said%20Tehran%20had%20already%20responded%20to%20Israeli%20threats%2C%20and%20didn't%20blame%20the%20Jewish%20state%20for%20the%20latest%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsfahan%20is%20home%20to%20around%202%20million%20people%20and%20several%20military%20bases%20and%20facilities.%20It's%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20one%20of%20several%20launch%20sites%20for%20Iran's%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20Saturday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20said%20two%20Israeli%20officials%20confirmed%20their%20nation%20was%20behind%20the%20strike.%20The%20newspaper%20also%20reported%20a%20military%20air%20base%20near%20Isfahan%20was%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20notified%20the%20US%20on%20Thursday%20it%20planned%20to%20retaliate%20in%20the%20next%2024-48%20hours%2C%20two%20American%20officials%20said%20to%20Bloomberg.%20They%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20private%20conversations.%20Spokespeople%20for%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20and%20the%20Pentagon%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrent%20crude%20oil%20climbed%20above%20%2490%20a%20barrel%20before%20trading%20around%20%2487.80%20as%20of%209%20a.m.%20in%20London%2C%20up%20less%20than%201%25%20on%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20also%20quickly%20reversed%20its%20jump.%20Yields%20on%2010-year%20US%20Treasuries%20%E2%80%94%20another%20haven%20for%20global%20investors%20in%20times%20of%20geopolitical%20stress%20%E2%80%94%20fell%20around%20four%20basis%20points%20to%204.59%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shekel%20weakened%20this%20week%20to%20its%20lowest%20level%20in%202024%2C%20though%20was%20steady%20on%20Friday%20at%203.78%20per%20dollar.%20That%20was%20despite%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Ratings%20downgrading%20Israel%20by%20one%20level%20to%20A%2B%20%E2%80%94%20still%20easily%20in%20investment-grade%20territory%20%E2%80%94%20hours%20before%20the%20reported%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20had%20vowed%20to%20retaliate%20against%20Iran%20for%20its%20barrage%20of%20more%20than%20300%20drones%20and%20missiles%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20which%20were%20destroyed%20before%20hitting%20their%20targets.%20While%20there%20was%20limited%20damage%20and%20no%20one%20was%20killed%2C%20Israel%20said%20it%20would%20send%20a%20message%20of%20weakness%20to%20Iran%20and%20its%20other%20enemies%20if%20it%20didn't%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20said%20it%20was%20a%20justified%20reaction%20to%20a%20strike%20on%20its%20embassy%20compound%20in%20Syria%20on%20April%201%2C%20which%20killed%20several%20Iranian%20officers%20and%20was%20blamed%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20Europe%20and%20Arab%20states%20urged%20Netanyahu%20to%20act%20with%20restraint.%20The%20foreign%20ministers%20of%20the%20UK%20and%20Germany%20both%20traveled%20to%20Israel%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20see%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20faced%20a%20dilemma%20this%20week.%20While%20many%20of%20his%20far-right%20coalition%20members%20insisted%20on%20a%20firm%20response%2C%20the%20Israeli%20public%20was%20split%20on%20whether%20the%20country%20should%20react%20at%20all.%20Many%2C%20according%20to%20a%20poll%2C%20said%20it%20wasn't%20worth%20provoking%20Iran%20and%20straining%20Israel's%20ties%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20more%20than%20six%20months%20into%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20still%20intent%20on%20attacking%20the%20city%20of%20Rafah%2C%20where%20it%20says%20several%20thousand%20Hamas%20fighters%20are%20lodged.%20Many%20in%20the%20country%20want%20the%20government%20to%20focus%20on%20finishing%20the%20conflict%20against%20the%20Iran-backed%20militant%20group%20that%20launched%20a%20deadly%20invasion%20on%20Oct.%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cst