ame-seeking%20influencers%20and%20YouTubers%20who%20inhabit%20a%20world%20of%20their%20own%20for%20better%20or%20for%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flove-sex-aur-dhoka-2-trailer-into-the-deep-dark-digital-world-5427690%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20the%20many%20ways%20in%20which%20violence%2C%20physical%20and%20psychological%2C%20is%20perpetrated%20on%20those%20who%20exist%20within%20the%20heady%20bubble%20and%20also%20on%20those%20who%20live%20outside%20it.%20This%20outright%20stumper%20of%20a%20film%20embraces%20its%20campy%2C%20pulpy%20spirit%20with%20all%20its%20might%20as%20it%20satirizes%20society%20that%20is%20led%20by%20technology%20in%20directions%20that%20it%20cannot%20fully%20grasp%2C%20not%20as%20yet%20at%20nay%20rate.%20By%20the%20time%20%3Cem%3ELSD%203%3C%2Fem%3E%20happens%2C%20we%20will%20probably%20know%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flove-sex-aur-dhoka-2-trailer-into-the-deep-dark-digital-world-5427690%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20raises%20questions%2C%20some%20playful%2C%20others%20pointed%2C%20even%20profound%2C%20about%20a%20world%20in%20which%20fake%2C%20nearly%20always%2C%20trumps%20fact.%20There%20is%20a%20heavy%20price%20to%20be%20paid%20for%20the%20surrender%20to%20the%20lure%20of%20constantly%20evolving%20technology%2C%20as%20the%20three%20principal%20characters%20in%20the%20film%20discover%20mostly%20at%20their%20own%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWritten%20by%20director%20and%20co-producer%20Dibakar%20Banerjee%20with%20Prateek%20Vats%20and%20Shubham%20(the%20writers%20of%20Eeb%20Allay%20Ooo!)%2C%20the%20Ekta%20Kapoor-produced%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20repeats%20the%20three-part%20interlinked%20structure%20of%20%3Cem%3ELSD%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20made%20nearly%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20ago%20and%20addressed%20the%20impact%20of%20recording%20devices%20that%20impinged%20on%20people's%20privacy%20and%20endangered%20their%20lives%20and%20mental%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2014%20years%20that%20have%20elapsed%20between%20the%20two%20films%2C%20both%20the%20hardware%20and%20the%20software%20have%20evolved%20to%20a%20point%20where%20the%20line%20between%20the%20real%20and%20the%20virtual%2C%20and%20the%20tangible%20and%20the%20deepfake%2C%20can%20be%20erased%20at%20the%20push%20of%20a%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20appears%20to%20thrive%20on%20leading%20double%20lives%20but%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20vanishing%20margins%20between%20the%20imagined%20and%20the%20factual%2C%20many%20are%20increasingly%20falling%20prey%20to%20manipulation%20and%20the%20danger%20of%20self-harm.%20That%20is%20the%20principal%20thematic%20burden%20of%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20although%20it%20isn't%20in%20the%20least%20interested%20in%20telling%20the%20audience%20what%20to%20make%20of%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20people%20it%20is%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExploring%20gender%20fluidity%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20isn't%20remotely%20self-conscious%2C%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20replaces%20the%20subheads%20of%20Love%2C%20Sex%20and%20Dhokha%20with%20Like%2C%20Share%20and%20Download.%20Each%20segment%20portrays%20the%20struggles%20of%20individuals%20trying%20to%20leap%20out%20of%20the%20boxes%20that%20a%20myopic%20society%20shoves%20them%20into%2C%20then%20slams%20the%20lid%20shut%20and%20keeps%20strict%20vigil%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20segment%2C%20a%20transwoman%2C%20Noor%20(Paritosh%20Tiwari)%2C%20who%20aspires%20to%20be%20an%20acclaimed%20actress%2C%20is%20a%20participant%20in%20a%20garish%20reality%20show%20-%20it%20is%20called%20Truth%20Ya%20Naach.%20It%20requires%20her%20to%20put%20her%20life%20under%20the%20public%20spotlight.%20Noor%20goes%20on%20and%20off%20camera%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20higher%20ratings%20as%20her%20rivals%20snap%20at%20her%20heels%20and%20keep%20her%20on%20her%20toes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20producers%20of%20the%20show%20-%20in%20the%20judges'%20seats%20are%20Sophie%20Chaudhry%2C%20Tusshar%20Kapoor%20and%20Anu%20Malik%20(the%20only%20one%20of%20the%20three%20who%20does%20not%20play%20himself)%20-%20manipulate%20her%20into%20a%20reunion%20with%20her%20estranged%20mother%20(Swaroopa%20Ghosh).%20The%20mother's%20first%20reaction%20on%20seeing%20Noor%20after%20a%20two-year%20hiatus%20is%20%26quot%3Bdublaa%20ho%20gaya%20hai%26quot%3B.%20She%20is%20still%20averse%20to%20accepting%20her%20altered%20sexual%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnu%20Malik's%20character%20throws%20a%20fit%20when%20the%20mother%20croons%20and%20the%20daughter%20dances%20to%20the%20song.%20Ordering%20the%20duo%20to%20stop%2C%20he%20thunders%3A%20%26quot%3BMaa%20se%20badhkar%20kuch%20nahin%20hain%26quot%3B.%20He%20follows%20that%20up%20with%20a%20mushy%20ode%20to%20motherhood.%20It%20is%20apparent%20that%20his%20outburst%20is%20scripted.%20The%20ratings%20go%20through%20the%20roof%20and%20it%20is%20revealed%20that%20this%20bit%20of%20the%20show%20has%20been%20sponsored%20%26quot%3BMaa%20Ki%20Mamta%20Aata%20(Mother's%20Love%20Flour).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20ratings%20and%20the%20truth%20meter%20-%20a%20method%20to%20measure%20the%20veracity%20of%20statements%20that%20the%20participants%20make%20on%20the%20show%20-%20yo-yo-ing%20wildly%2C%20Noor%20is%20under%20constant%20pressure%20to%20'perform'%20her%20transition%20for%20the%20consumption%20of%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20process%20of%20gender%20assertion%20is%20reduced%20to%20a%20game%20controlled%20by%20the%20producers%20of%20the%20show%2C%20the%20sponsors%2C%20the%20public%20at%20large%20and%2C%20last%20but%20not%20the%20least%2C%20the%20anti-vulgarity%20clause%20in%20the%20rules%20that%20govern%20broadcasting.%20Technology%20and%20a%20society%20that%20is%20in%20voyeuristic%20mode%2024%2F7%2C%20personal%20desire%20has%20been%20snatched%20away%20by%20the%20collective%20will%20of%20those%20whose%20''likes%26quot%3B%20can%20make%20or%20break%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20too%2C%20has%20a%20third-gender%20character%2C%20Kulu%20(Bonita%20Rajpurohit)%2C%20struggling%20with%20the%20consequences%20of%20being%20who%20she%20is.%20She%20is%20strapped%20for%20cash%20and%20unapologetic%20about%20using%20her%20body%20to%20earn%20her%20a%20few%20rupees%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKulu%20works%20on%20the%20cleaning%20team%20at%20a%20Metro%20Rail%20station%20in%20Delhi.%20Her%20boss%2C%20Lovina%20Singh%20(Swastika%20Mukherjee)%2C%20single%20mother%20of%20a%20school-going%20boy%20(who%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20the%20link%20between%20this%20story%20and%20the%20next)%2C%20feigns%20sympathy%20for%20her%20employee%20when%20she%20gets%20into%20serious%20trouble%20and%20is%20in%20danger%20of%20losing%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20mounting%20pressure%20from%20the%20head%20honcho%2C%20Lovina%20does%20her%20best%20to%20control%20the%20damage%20that%20the%20negative%20publicity%20for%20her%20company%20-%20which%20seeks%20mileage%20out%20of%20giving%20employment%20to%20transgenders%20-%20but%20with%20every%20move%20that%20she%20makes%20she%20only%20succeeds%20in%20exposing%20her%20own%20and%20her%20firm's%20double%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20only%20in%20the%20virtual%20world%20that%20things%20are%20phony.%20In%20fact%2C%20if%20things%20are%20fake%20in%20the%20images%20and%20claims%20that%20float%20around%20in%20a%20hyper-connected%20universe%2C%20they%20are%20only%20a%20reflection%20of%20all%20the%20pretence%20that%20is%20constantly%20sought%20to%20be%20passed%20off%20as%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20exactly%20what%2018-year-old%20school%20boy%20Shubham%20Narang%20(Abhinav%20Singh)%2C%20Game%20Paapi%20in%20the%20virtual%20world%2C%20does%20in%20his%20avatar%20as%20a%20hyper-masculine%20dude.%20Artificial%20intelligence%2C%20virtual%20reality%20and%20metaverses%20have%20flip%20sides%20that%20extract%20a%20high%20price%20from%20those%20who%20play%20along%20and%20lose%20themselves%20in%20the%20dead-end%20algorithm-driven%20labyrinths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20great%20thing%20about%20a%20Dibakar%20Banerjee%20film%20is%20that%20it%20never%20fails%20to%20spring%20surprises.%20LSD%202%20has%20more%20than%20its%20share%20of%20fearless%20flights%20of%20fancy.%20Some%20land%2C%20some%20don't.%20But%20that%20takes%20little%20away.%20Even%20when%20it%20tends%20to%20be%20baffling%2C%20the%20film%20makes%20you%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20cinema%20that%20excites%20you%2C%20%3Cem%3ELSD%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20might%20be%20well%20worth%20your%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713518340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F75568sto_lsd2_625x300_19_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flove-sex-aur-dhokha-2-review-outright-stumper-of-a-film-embraces-its-campy-pulpy-spirit-3-stars-5476524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Love%20Sex%20Aur%20Dhokha%202%20Review%3A%20The%20great%20thing%20about%20a%20Dibakar%20Banerjee%20film%20is%20that%20it%20never%20fails%20to%20spring%20surprises.%20LSD%202%20has%20more%20than%20its%20share%20of%20fearless%20flights%20of%20fancy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Flove-sex-aur-dhokha-2-review-outright-stumper-of-a-film-embraces-its-campy-pulpy-spirit-3-stars-5476524%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Allman%20Brothers%20Band%20guitarist%20Betts%20dies%20at%2080%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713518254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10A99%2Fproduction%2F_133194286_gettyimages-167649593_2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68853477%230%22%2C%22summa