2%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20New%20York%20real-estate%20agent%20who's%20not%20worried%20about%20losing%20guaranteed%20commission.%20Here's%20what%20I'm%20doing%20to%20replace%20those%20funds.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mukul%20Lalchandani%20is%20sitting%20and%20smiling%20in%20his%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66205b4b10c6b0cde5f08ce1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mukul%20Lalchandani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMukul%20Lalchandani%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20agent%2C%20discusses%20the%20impact%20of%20new%20commission%20rules.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20rules%20mean%20that%20sellers%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20buyer's%20agent%20commission.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20changes%20may%20most%20affect%20low-income%20buyers%2C%20but%20Lalchandani%20says%20his%20clients%20won't%20be%20affected.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Mukul%20Lalchandani%2C%20a%2044-year-old%20real-estate%20agent%20from%20New%20York.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20wanted%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20in%20the%20US%20before%20immigrating%20here%20from%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20but%20they%20didn't%20know%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-find-real-estate-agent%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20real%20estate%20worked%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20working%20with%20the%20seller's%20broker%20and%20didn't%20realize%20they%20could%20work%20with%20a%20buyer's%20broker%20who%20would%20help%20them%20find%20the%20best%20deal.%20The%20seller's%20broker%20deceived%20them.%20They%20ended%20up%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20had%20no%20house%20to%20move%20into%20when%20they%20arrived%20in%20the%20US.%20I%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20so%20I%20could%20prevent%20other%20immigrant%20families%20from%20going%20through%20the%20same%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lived%20in%20New%20York%20for%2023%20years%20and%20have%20been%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20for%20over%2015%20years.%20I%20established%20my%20own%20agency%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undividedre.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUndivided%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20realtors%20in%20NY%20are%20not%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F03%2F21%2Frealestate%2Fnar-rebny-new-york-buying-selling.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBut%2520in%2520New%2520York%2520City%2Cto%2520the%2520group%2527s%2520amended%2520rules.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Association%20of%20Realtors%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20association%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rebny.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EREBNY%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20NAR%20and%20real-estate%20agents%20all%20around%20the%20country%20are%20preparing%20for%20new%20rules%20to%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20rules%20is%20that%20the%20seller%20no%20longer%20has%20to%20pay%20a%20commission%20to%20the%20buyer's%20agent.%20REBNY%20already%20implemented%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rebny.com%2Farticles%2Fdecoupling-commissions-faq%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20rules%20starting%20January%201%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20the%20new%20rules%20were%20a%20shock%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20While%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20is%20preparing%20for%20the%20rule%20changes%2C%20we're%20already%20seeing%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20agency%20has%20had%20to%20implement%20new%20policies%20to%20address%20the%20changes%20brought%20on%20by%20these%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20what%20the%20new%20commission%20rules%20mean%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20confusion%20around%20the%20commission%20rule%20and%20what%20it%20means%2C%20especially%20for%20buyers.%20The%20rules%20were%20made%20as%20part%20of%20a%20settlement%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-antitrust-lawsuits-verdict-agent-commissions-nar-future-homebuying-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20nationwide%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20someone%20sells%20a%20property%2C%20they%20must%20pay%20their%20broker%20and%20the%20buyer's%20broker%20a%20commission.%20It's%20not%20fair%20to%20the%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rules%20will%20mean%20that%20the%20buyer%20will%20have%20to%20either%20pay%20for%20their%20own%20broker%20or%20not%20use%20a%20broker%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20implemented%20two%20major%20policies%20in%20my%20agency%20to%20help%20with%20the%20confusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20sit%20down%20with%20each%20buyer%20and%20explain%20to%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-housing-market-homebuying-agents-commissions-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20the%20new%20rules%20affect%20them%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20first%2C%20my%20clients%20are%20confused.%20Then%2C%20when%20it%20clicks%2C%20they're%20shocked.%20They%20realize%20they%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20broker%20themselves.%20They%20have%20an%20extra%20cost%20for%20buying%20the%20property%20which%20they%20didn't%20consider%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20agency%20has%20also%20begun%20requiring%20all%20new%20buyers%20to%20sign%20an%20%26quot%3Bexclusive%20buyers%20agreement.%26quot%3B%20In%20this%20agreement%2C%20we%20outline%20everything%20we%20will%20do%20to%20help%20the%20buyer%20through%20the%20buying%20process%20in%20their%20best%20interest.%20It%20also%20states%20how%20much%20they'll%20pay%20us%20for%20our%20services.%20This%20contract%20helps%20clarify%20the%20terms%20and%20payment%20and%20prevents%20any%20confusion%20related%20to%20the%20new%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20implement%20this%20contract%20and%20charge%20our%20clients%20a%20fee%20because%20we%20no%20longer%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frealtors-real-estate-agent-commission-home-housing-sales-ripoff-cost-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20commission%20from%20the%20seller%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20buyers%20are%20shocked%2C%20but%20this%20will%20affect%20low-income%20buyers%20the%20most%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20agency%20is%20a%20boutique%20agency%20in%20NY%2C%20and%20my%20clients%20tend%20to%20be%20high-networth%20individuals.%20The%20buyers%20who%20come%20to%20me%20are%20shocked%20when%20they%20learn%20about%20the%20new%20fees%20but%20can%20afford%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReal-estate%20investors%20want%20a%20broker%20to%20find%20the%20best%20property%20for%20them%2C%20so%20they'll%20also%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20the%20commission%20fees.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnewyork.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fover-a-third-of-nyc-homes-for-sale-get-taken-off-market-without-finding-a-buyer-survey%2F4813867%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNYC%2520real%2520estate%2520has%2520never%2Caverage%2520of%2520just%252015%2520days.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuying%20in%20NY%20is%20especially%20complicated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20buyers%20really%20need%20a%20broker.%20The%20new%20commission%20rule%20will%20not%20hurt%20people%20looking%20to%20buy%20expensive%20homes%20or%20investment%20properties.%20It%20will%20hurt%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzandi-moodys-house-prices-mortgage-interest-rates-affordability-crisis-market-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower-income%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20a%20property%20without%20a%20broker%20is%20possible%2C%20but%20the%20buyer%20is%20taking%20a%20risk.%20Higher-income%20buyers%20such%20as%20foreigners%20and%20out-of-towners%20who%20buy%20real%20estate%20in%20NY%20will%20avoid%20the%20risk%20and%20pay%20the%20broker%20fees%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20get%20a%20good%20deal.%20However%2C%20lower-income%20buyers%20around%20the%20country%20may%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-affordability-homebuyer-earnings-income-price-trends-covid-comparison-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20a%20broker%3C%2Fa%3E%20anymore.%20That%20means%20they'll%20be%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20getting%20into%20a%20bad%20real-estate%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20someone%20is%20buying%20a%20million-dollar%20home%2C%20they%20would%20need%20about%20%2415%2C000%20to%20pay%20the%20broker%20now.%20That%20can't%20come%20out%20of%20pocket%20for%20most%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20Brokers%20will%20leave%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20some%20jobs%20will%20disappear%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20means%20that%20many%20brokers%20who%20sell%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20properties%20a%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbad-real-estate-agents-realtors-homebuyers-sellers-housing-market-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewill%20leave%20the%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Only%20brokers%20who%20work%20in%20real%20estate%20as%20their%20main%20source%20of%20income%20will%20be%20able%20to%20survive%20the%20new%20rules.%20Buyers%20will%20only%20pay%20for%20the%20brokers%20who%20have%20the%20most%20experience%20and%20get%20the%20best%20deals.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20we%20could%20also%20see%20bonuses%20for%20the%20buyer's%20brokers%20in%20a%20slow%20market%20that%20may%20not%20be%20offered%20in%20a%20hot%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20might%20even%20see%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-rule-of-home-buying-fire-your-real-estate-agent-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20of%20a%20buyer's%20broker%20disappear%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20few%20years.%20There%20used%20to%20be%20tenant%20agents%20who%20helped%20people%20find%20places%20to%20rent.%20That%20job%20disappeared%20when%20people%20looking%20to%20rent%20began%20talking%20directly%20with%20companies%20that%20own%20the%20properties.%20This%20could%20happen%20to%20the%20buyer's%20agent%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20confused%20about%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20it's%20because%20they're%20confusing.%20Sellers%20were%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20previous%20rules%20where%20they%20had%20to%20represent%20the%20buyer's%20best%20interest%20by%20paying%20a%20commission%20to%20the%20buyer's%20broker.%20They'll%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rules%20will%20have%20big%20ramifications%20as%20buyers%20start%20experiencing%20the%20changing%20real%20estate%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agent-discusses-new-home-buying-rules-housing-market-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713517561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66205b7549058e669357233c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agent-discusses-new-home-buying-rules-housing-market-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20New%20York%20real-estate%20agent%20isn't%20worried%20about%20sellers%20not%20paying%20commission.%20He's%20already%20implemented%20two%20new%20policies%20to%20replace%20those%20funds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ananya%20Vahal)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agent-discusses-new-home-buying-rules-housing-market-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20did%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20avoid%20to%20infl