%20width%3D%5C%221983%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tan%20interior%20of%20a%20Jeep%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6621465c49058e6693574be8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221487%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20the%20Jeep.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Vincent%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20shopping%2C%20I%20considered%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-tax-credit-changes-fewer-models-eligible-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etax%20credits%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20available%20at%20the%20time.%20There%20was%20a%20full%20%247%2C500%20credit%2C%20and%20it%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20sense%20because%20of%20how%20we%20use%20the%20vehicle.%20The%20credit%20is%20not%20available%20anymore%2C%20but%20you%20can%20get%20some%20state%2C%20local%2C%20and%20utility%20credits%20for%20operating%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20drives%20the%20car%20about%20half%20the%20time%20and%20can%20drive%20it%20to%20work%20and%20back%20daily%20on%20electricity%20alone.%20I%20think%20I%20only%20put%20four%20gas%20tanks%20in%20it%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20only%20reason%20I%20had%20to%20put%20gas%20in%20it%20was%20to%20protect%20the%20engine%20and%20the%20fuel%20delivery%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhonda-odyssey-review-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHonda%20Odyssey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20better%20for%20our%20dog.%20The%20Jeep%20is%20pretty%20high%2C%20and%20the%20dog%20weighs%2050%20pounds%2C%20so%20lifting%20the%20dog%20up%20and%20down%20in%20the%20SUV%20is%20difficult.%20With%20the%20minivan%2C%20the%20dog%20can%20just%20hop%20up%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20drive%20a%20high-trim%20model%2C%20the%20Summit%2C%20so%20it%20is%20basically%20a%20luxury%20SUV.%20The%20luxury%20model%20package%2C%20which%20costs%20around%20%2413%2C000%20more%20than%20the%20base%20model%2C%20has%20massaging%20seats%20and%20a%20great%20navigation%20system%2C%20as%20well%20as%20night%20vision%20for%20when%20we're%20on%20rural%20country%20roads%2C%20so%20it's%20pretty%20well-loaded.%20The%20only%20thing%20I%20wish%20it%20had%20that%20it%20doesn't%20is%20a%20lower%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20Jeep%20can%20off-road%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20done%20it%20yet.%20The%20number%20of%20miles%20we%20put%20on%20it%20is%20limited%20because%20I%20test%20other%20cars%2C%20but%20most%20of%20the%20miles%20I%20put%20on%20this%20Jeep%20are%20electric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDriving%20electric%20with%20the%20hybrid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20screen%20inside%20of%20a%20Jeep%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662146cc10c6b0cde5f0b780%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20charge%20rate.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Vincent%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20drive%20outside%20commuting%20and%20exceed%20its%20electric-only%20range%2C%20it%20operates%20like%20a%20normal%20hybrid%20and%20still%20gets%20great%20mileage%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20reliant%20on%20an%20EV%20charger%20all%20the%20time%2C%20like%20with%20a%20pure%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Grand%20Cherokee%20is%20a%20great%20vehicle%2C%20but%20with%20gas-only%20power%20the%20mileage%20is%20terrible%2C%20so%20the%204xe%20gets%20good%20mileage%20for%20a%20midsize%20SUV%20because%20it's%20a%20hybrid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20perfect%20world%2C%20you%20never%20notice%20the%20transitions%20between%20running%20on%20gas%2C%20running%20as%20a%20hybrid%2C%20or%20running%20as%20electric.%20In%20reality%2C%20you%20do%20feel%20those%20transitions%20in%20the%20Jeep%20more%20than%20you%20do%20in%20some%20other%20vehicles%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20obtrusive%2C%20and%20I%20learned%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20thing%20I've%20noticed%20is%