nied%20that%20Iran%20had%20been%20attacked%20from%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Atomic%20Energy%20Agency%20confirmed%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20damage%26quot%3B%20to%20Iran's%20nuclear%20sites.%20%26quot%3BDG%20%40rafaelmgrossi%20continues%20to%20call%20for%20extreme%20restraint%20from%20everybody%20and%20reiterates%20that%20nuclear%20facilities%20should%20never%20be%20a%20target%20in%20military%20conflicts.%20IAEA%20is%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20very%20closely%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20New%20York%20Times%20report%20quoted%20Iranian%20officials%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20strike%20had%20hit%20a%20military%20air%20base%20near%20Isfahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20also%20coincided%20with%20the%2085th%20birthday%20of%20Iran's%20supreme%20leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khameini.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Iran%20Responded%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20state%20media%20reported%20that%20air%20defence%20systems%20over%20several%20cities%20in%20the%20country%20were%20activated%20early%20on%20Friday.%20Flights%20to%20Tehran%2C%20Isfahan%20and%20Shiraz%20were%20suspended%20and%20UAE-based%20flydubai%20airline%20cancelled%20flights%20to%20the%20country.%20Two%20Tehran%20airports%2C%20however%2C%20resumed%20service%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20AFP%2C%20flight%20tracking%20software%20showed%20commercial%20flights%20avoiding%20western%20Iran%2C%20including%20Isfahan.%20Iranian%20television%20carried%20a%20live%20feed%20of%20normal%20traffic%20conditions%20at%20a%20roundabout%20in%20Isfahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETasnim%20news%20agency%20reported%20that%20Iranian%20TV%20reported%20complete%20security%20and%20peace%20at%20the%20Isfahan%20nuclear%20site.%20It%20also%20said%20a%20senior%20army%20official%20in%20Isfahan%20had%20confirmed%20that%20the%20explosion%20heard%20in%20the%20province%20was%20due%20to%20the%20firing%20of%20anti-aircraft%20weapons%20targeting%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%20objects%26quot%3B.%20Dalirian%20said%20three%20drones%20were%20shot%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Isfahan%20Is%20Important%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsfahan%20houses%20nuclear%20experimental%20reactors%20and%20uranium%20conversion%20facilities.%20It%20is%20also%20home%20to%20Iran's%20underground%20Natanz%20enrichment%20site%2C%20which%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20targeted%20by%20suspected%20Israeli%20sabotage%20attacks%2C%20Associated%20Press%20reported.%20Isfahan%20also%20houses%20Iran's%20fleet%20of%20US-made%20F-14%20Tomcats%20that%20were%20bought%20before%20the%20Iranian%20Revolution%20in%201979.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhahjaworstan%2C%20where%20an%20explosion%20was%20heard%2C%20is%20located%20near%20Isfahan%20airport%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20eighth%20hunting%20base%20of%20the%20Army%20Air%20Force%26quot%3B%2C%20news%20agency%20FARS%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20in%20Isfahan%20is%20particularly%20significant%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Iran's%20warning%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20missile%20strike%20on%20Israel%2C%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20warned%20that%20it%20would%20attack%20Israel's%20nuclear%20sites%20and%20may%20pursue%20a%20nuclear%20weapon%20if%20the%20country%20strikes%20at%20Iran's%20nuclear%20facilities.%20%26quot%3BThe%20nuclear%20facilities%20of%20the%20Zionist%20enemy%20have%20been%20identified%20and%20all%20the%20necessary%20information%20from%20all%20targets%20is%20at%20our%20disposal%2C%26quot%3B%20Brigadier%20General%20Ahmad%20Haghtalab%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20Tasnim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20fingers%20are%20on%20the%20trigger%20of%20firing%20strong%20missiles%20to%20destroy%20the%20designated%20targets%20in%20response%20to%20a%20potential%20attack%20by%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20IRGC%20division%20that%20is%20tasked%20with%20protecting%20Iranian%20nuclear%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20fake%20Zionist%20regime%20wants%20to%20use%20the%20threat%20of%20attacking%20the%20nuclear%20centres%20of%20our%20country%20as%20a%20tool%2C%20reconsidering%20the%20doctrine%20and%20policies%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%2C%20and%20deviating%20from%20previously%20stated%20considerations%20would%20be%20likely%20and%20imaginable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%2C%20in%20what%20was%20Iran's%20most%20direct%20warning%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20not%20commented%20officially%20on%20the%20attack%20yet.%20Israeli%20military%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20a%20comment%20at%20this%20time.%26quot%3B%20Israel's%20national%20security%20minister%20Itamar%20Ben-Givir's%20one-word%20post%20on%20X%20read%2C%20%26quot%3Bweak%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20and%20Pentagon%2C%20too%2C%20are%20yet%20to%20make%20a%20statement.%20US%20media%20reports%20quoting%20officials%20have%20said%20Washington%20did%20receive%20an%20advance%20notice%20of%20the%20reported%20strike%2C%20but%20did%20not%20endorse%20it%20or%20play%20any%20part%20in%20its%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel%2C%20no%20official%20remark%20from%20Israel%20and%20the%20limited%20nature%20of%20the%20strike%20may%20provide%20Iran%20a%20position%20of%20strategic%20deniability%20-%20much%20needed%20for%20a%20de-escalation%20in%20the%20region.%20But%20if%20Israel%20comes%20on%20record%20to%20own%20up%20its%20role%20in%20the%20strike%2C%20all%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20how%20Iran%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20is%20watching%20with%20bated%20breath%20how%20the%20situation%20is%20unfolding%20in%20the%20sensitive%20region%2C%20where%20Israel%20is%20already%20waging%20a%20war%20in%20Gaza%20in%20retaliation%20to%20the%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20has%20warned%20that%20spiralling%20tensions%20over%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Iran's%20attack%20on%20Israel%20could%20devolve%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-scale%20regional%20conflict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Middle%20East%20is%20on%20a%20precipice.%20Recent%20days%20have%20seen%20a%20perilous%20escalation%20--%20in%20words%20and%20deeds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20told%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%20%26quot%3BOne%20miscalculation%2C%20one%20miscommunication%2C%20one%20mistake%2C%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20unthinkable%20---%20a%20full-scale%20regional%20conflict%20that%20would%20be%20devastating%20for%20all%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said%2C%20calling%20for%20restraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713515460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fk2quqlu_isfahan_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-conflict-isfahan-why-strike-on-isfahan-irans-nuclear-hub-may-step-up-west-asia-conflict-5475868%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%20has%20its%20fingers%20crossed%20as%20Iran's%20state%20media%20has%20reported%20explosions%20in%20the%20Isfahan%20province%2C%20days%20after%20Iran's%20drone%20attack%20on%20Israel%20sparked%20fears%20of%20a%20major%20escalation%20in%20West%20Asia%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-conflict-isfahan-why-strike-on-isfahan-irans-nuclear-hub-may-step-up-west-asia-conflict-5475868%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-conflict-isfahan-why-strike-on-isfahan-irans-nuclear-hub-may-step-up-west-asia-conflict-5475868%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-conflict-isfahan-why-strike-on-isfahan-irans-nuclear-hub-may-step-up-west-asia-conflict-5475868%2Famp%2F1%22%7D