n%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20met%20about%2025%20to%2030%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20spent%20many%20days%20with%20them.%20We%20wanted%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20soil%20they%20use%2C%20the%20process%20of%20cultivating%20saffron%2C%20how%20long%20it%20takes%2C%20and%20which%20temperatures%20saffron%20thrives%20in.%20We%20also%20bought%20the%20bulbs%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20back%2C%20Shubha%20set%20up%20a%20cold%20storage%20room%20of%20560%20square%20feet%20and%20started%20with%202%2C000%20kg%20of%20saffron%20bulbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20you%20grow%20saffron%20indoors%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345755%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-at-home-indoors-ramesh-gera-noida-akarshak-institute-online-course%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaffron%20bulbs%20from%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20look%20like%20garlic%20pods%2C%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20dry%20them%20in%20a%20room%20and%20later%20aerate%20them%20for%20three%20days.%20They%20had%20to%20be%20checked%2C%20cleaned%20and%20turned%20every%20few%20hours%20by%20hand%2C%20which%20is%20traditionally%20done%20by%20women%20in%20Kashmir.%20Each%20seed%20was%20checked%20for%20moisture%20and%20rot%2C%20and%20any%20extra%20skin%20was%20removed%20through%20a%20process%20called%20silvering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maintaining%20the%20right%20temperature%20is%20crucial%20in%20saffron%20cultivation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347648%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMaintaining%20the%20right%20temperature%20is%20crucial%20in%20saffron%20cultivation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20seeds%20were%20aerated%2C%20they%20were%20placed%20in%20a%20cold%20room%20in%20vertical%20trays%20on%20racks.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20should%20be%20no%20water%2C%20moisture%20or%20humidity%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bulbs%20started%20growing%20and%20buds%20emerged%20after%20a%20few%20days.%20Then%2C%20the%20challenge%20was%20to%20know%20when%20to%20provide%20light%20to%20the%20buds%20and%20at%20what%20temperature.%20While%20the%20beautiful%20valleys%20of%20Kashmir%20provide%20the%20perfect%20ambience%20which%20the%20buds%20enjoy%2C%20replicating%20them%201%2C200%20km%20away%20was%20a%20massive%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20bud%20receives%20light%20only%20when%20it%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20soil.%20Learning%20at%20what%20stage%20that%20happens%20and%20providing%20the%20right%20temperature%20was%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20When%20we%20started%2C%20we%20placed%20bulbs%20in%2018%20racks%20in%20six%20rows%20and%20provided%20different%20temperatures%20and%20light%20to%20each%20rack%20to%20judge%20which%20one%20worked%20the%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20this%2C%20Shubha%20and%20Ankit%20went%20through%2010%20years%20of%20saffron%20production%20data%20in%20Kashmir.%20They%20found%20that%20the%20best%20harvest%20was%20achieved%20in%202015-16%20and%20replicated%20the%20temperatures%20of%20that%20year.%20They%20developed%20a%20programme%20using%20IoT%20devices%20and%20sensors%20to%20maintain%20the%20right%20conditions%20and%20a%20controlled%20environment%20through%20aeroponics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20about%2060%20days%2C%20the%20beautiful%20purple%20flower%20emerged%20and%20was%20ready%20for%20harvest!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20saffron%20from%20Shubhavni%20farms%20is%20sold%20online%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347647%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20saffron%20from%20Shubhavni%20farms%20is%20sold%20online%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20saffron%20flower%20has%20three%20components%20%E2%80%94%20the%20stigma%2C%20which%20is%20used%20for%20consumption%3B%20the%20stamen%2C%20which%20is%20yellow%20and%20used%20in%20the%20textile%20industry%3B%20and%20the%20petals%2C%20which%20are%20purple%20and%20used%20in%20the%20textile%20industry%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20harvested%2C%20the%20stigma%2C%20more%20commonly%20known%20as%20saffron%2C%20must%20undergo%20drying%20and%20packaging.%20Shubhavni%20sells%20one%20gram%20of%20saffron%20for%20Rs%20750.%20They%20are%20currently%20conducting%20online%20sales%2C%20with%20total%20sales%20amounting%20to%20Rs%208%20lakh%20thus%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ankit%20developed%20the%20system%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20Shubha%20who%20maintains%20it%20and%20oversees%20the%20business.%20She%20learned%20about%20the%20technology%20employed%2C%20computer%20handling%2C%20the%20art%20of%20sales%2C%20and%20much%20more.%20She%20smiles%20as%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20age%20limit%20to%20learning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20now%20plans%20to%20multiply%20production%20by%20tripling%20the%20area%20under%20production.%20She%20also%20wants%20to%20try%20for%20two%20harvests%20in%20a%20year%2C%20while%20typically%20only%20one%20harvest%20is%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20advantage%20of%20growing%20saffron%20indoors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubha%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20people%20leading%20the%20shift%20towards%20indoor%20agriculture%2C%20especially%20in%20saffron.%20Many%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20too%20are%20making%20this%20switch%2C%20as%20climate%20change%20has%20severely%20hampered%20their%20saffron%20production.%20A%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%20that%20the%20area%20under%20saffron%20cultivation%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20reduced%20from%205%2C707%20hectares%20in%201996%20to%201%2C116%20hectares%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shubha%20is%20providing%20employment%20to%2020%20women%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347653%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShubha%20is%20providing%20employment%20to%2020%20women%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndoor%20farming%20isn%E2%80%99t%20threatened%20by%20climate%20change%2C%20soil%20issues%20or%20developments%20nearby.%20It%20is%20essentially%20foolproof%20if%20one%20masters%20the%20art%20of%20maintaining%20the%20right%20temperature%20and%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20advantage%20is%20the%20space%20needed%20for%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CA%20farmer%20would%20typically%20sow%202%2C000%20kg%20of%20saffron%20in%201.5%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20while%20we%20are%20able%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20560%20square%20feet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ankit%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubha%20wants%20to%20create%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338349%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-with-aeroponics-online-classes-himachal-pradesh-solan-mushrooms%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaffron%20%E2%80%9Crevolution%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20help%20more%20people%20grow%20the%20spice%20indoors.%20Through%20her%20venture%2C%20she%20is%20currently%20providing%20employment%20to%20over%2020%20women%20in%20Mainpuri%2C%20as%20the%20process%20of%20growing%20saffron%20is%20laborious.%20Right%20from%20drying%20the%20bulbs%20to%20plucking%20each%20stigma%2C%20drying%2C%20and%20packing%20them%2C%20it%20requires%20careful%20and%20precise%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Geeta%20Devi%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20dependable%20income.%20At%2040%20years%20old%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20a%20mother%20of%20five%20and%20the%20primary%20provider%20for%20her%20family.%20Previously%2C%20she%20laboured%20in%20the%20fields%20under%20the%20scorching%20sun%2C%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20Work%20was%20inconsistent%2C%20and%20income%20was%20meagre%2C%20she%20recalls.%20However%2C%20since%20joining%20Shubhavni%20Farms%20last%20July%2C%20her%20situation%20has%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20enjoy%20the%20work%20here%20and%20brought%20in%2020%20more%20women.%20We%20were%20taught%20everything%20about%20saffron%20cultivation%20and%20did%20everything%20from%20aeration%20to%20keeping%20it%20clean%20and%20removing%20the%20stamen%20from%20the%20flower.%20We%20are%20working%20in%20a%20comfortable%20environment%20instead%20of%20bearing%20the%20harsh%20heat.%20We%20get%20paid%20at%20least%20Rs%20100%20more%20per%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Geeta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20Shubha%E2%80%99s%20dream%20to%20provide%20a%20regular%20source%20of%20income%20to%20more%20women%20like%20Geeta%20and%20ensure%20that%20their%20children%20have%20a%20better%20future.%20And%20to%20every%20woman%20wanting%20to%20start%20a%20business%2C%20she%20has%20one%20message%2C%20%E2%80%9CNever%20underestimate%20yourself%20and%20your%20dreams.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20we%20are%20no%20longer%20a%20patriarchal%20society.%20We%20are%20equally%20capable.%20Self-reliance%20gives%20immense%20confidence%20and%20gives%20you%20an%20opportunity%20to%20inspire%20others.%20Even%20starting%20a%20small%20business%20will%20boost%20your%20happiness%20level%20and%20morale%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shubha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Bhatnagar%20family%E2%80%99s%20dinner