a%20political%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact-check%20titled%20'PTI%20Fact%20Check%3A%20No%2C%20Aamir%20Khan%20didn't%20endorse%20any%20political%20party%3B%20edited%20video%20with%20AI%20voice%20clone%20shared%20on%20social%20media'%20can%20be%20read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Ffact-detail%2FNo--Aamir-Khan-didn-t-endorse-any-political-party%253B-edited-video-with-AI-voice-clone-shared-on-social-media%2F1433707%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClaim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Instagram%20user%20shared%20on%20April%2015%20a%20video%20of%20actor%20Aamir%20Khan%20talking%20about%20two%20types%20of%20guarantees%20given%20to%20the%20citizens%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caption%20of%20the%20post%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BAamir%20khan%20ne%202024%20Election%20Ko%20le%20kar%20kya%20kaha%2C%20Ki%20Abki%20baar%20Congress%20ko%20vote%20do%20%23news%20%23aamirkhan%20%23election%20%23bollywood%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5wOC05SrSf%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fperma.cc%2F2F4F-2WDN%5C%22%3Earchive%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20post%20and%20below%20is%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20same%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20in%20the%20video%2C%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20two%20types%20of%20guarantees%20in%20these%20elections%20-%20good%20and%20bad.%20The%20bad%20news%20is%20that%20once%20again%2C%20'jumle%20waade'%20(catchphrase%20promises)%20have%20been%20made%20to%20ruin%20your%20life.%20But%20the%20good%20news%20is%20that%20this%20time%2C%20there%20are%20'5%20Nyay'%20(five%20justices)%20for%20your%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20the%20video%20featured%20Congress%20party's%20logo%20with%20the%20text%20'Vote%20for%20Nyay%2C%20Vote%20for%20Congress'.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvestigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20the%20investigation%2C%20the%20Desk%20watched%20the%20viral%20video%20and%20noticed%20a%20lip-sync%20issue%20in%20it.%20We%20then%20uploaded%20the%20viral%20video%20to%20the%20InVid%20Tool%20Search%20and%20received%20a%20few%20keyframes.%20Further%2C%20scanning%20those%20keyframes%20through%20Google%20Lens%2C%20the%20Desk%20found%20a%20Twitter%20post%20shared%20on%20April%2015%2C%20which%20carried%20the%20same%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fravishumar146%2Fstatus%2F1779593749229891596%5C%22%3Ethe%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fsave%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fravishumar146%2Fstatus%2F1779593749229891596%5C%22%3Earchive%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20below%20is%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20same%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20further%20scanning%20the%20Google%20Lens%20search%20results%2C%20the%20Desk%20found%20that%20a%20similar%20video%20was%20uploaded%20on%20YouTube%20from%20the%20official%20channel%20of%20'Satyamev%20Jayate'%2C%20a%20chat%20show%20hosted%20by%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20which%20was%20telecasted%20on%20Star%20Plus%20channel.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbJyQ9NhZCtk%5C%22%3Ethe%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20video%20titled%2C%20%26quot%3BSatyamev%20Jayate%20S1%20%7C%20Episode%2013%20%7C%20The%20Idea%20of%20India%20%7C%20Liberty%20(Hindi)%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20was%20published%20on%20August%2030%2C%202016%2C%20and%20below%20is%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20same%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20description%20of%20the%20video%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BStay%20tuned%20to%20the%20new%20season%20of%20Satyamev%20Jayate%2C%20starting%20March%202%2C%20every%20Sunday%2C%2011%20AM%20onwards%20only%20on%20STAR%20Plus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Desk%20noticed%20that%20Khan's%20outfit%20and%20the%20red%20glowing%20light%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20video%20was%20the%20same%20as%20in%20the%20viral%20video.%20Below%20is%20a%20combination%20image%2C%20comparing%20the%20visuals%20of%20the%20two%20videos%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Desk%20listened%20to%20this%2040-second%20video%20and%20noticed%20that%20the%20actor's%20statement%20differed%20from%20what%20it%20was%20in%20the%20viral%20video.%20He%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20that%20that%20he%20will%20be%20coming%20again%20for%20a%20new%20season%20with%20five%20episodes%2C%20which%20will%20be%20telecasted%20on%20Sundays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20English%20translation%20of%20what%20Khan%20said%20in%20the%20promo%20video%2C%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BFriends%20I%20have%20two%20news%20for%20you%2C%20one%20is%20good%20and%20other%20is%20bad.%20The%20bad%20news%20is%20that%20I%20am%20coming%20back%20again%20to%20spoil%20your%20Sunday.%20But%20the%20good%20news%20is%20that%20I%20will%20only%20spoil%20your%205%20Sundays.....%20only%205%20Every%20Sunday%20of%20March%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20cue%20from%20this%2C%20the%20Desk%20scanned%20the%20official%20website%20of%20Satyamev%20Jayate%20and%20found%20that%20the%20above-mentioned%20video%20was%20the%20promo%20for%20Season%202%2C%20Episode%201%2C%20titled%20'Fighting%20Rape'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.satyamevjayate.in%2FFighting-Rape%2FEPISODE-1watchvideo.aspx%3Fuid%3Dsmj_sundaypromo%5C%22%3Ethe%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20official%20website%20and%20below%20is%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20same%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt2360717%2Fepisodes%2F%3Fseason%3D2%5C%22%3EIMDb%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20mentions%20that%20the%20first%20episode%20of%20Season%202%20was%20telecast%20on%20March%205%2C%202014.%20Below%20is%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20same%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20Desk%20concluded%20that%20a%20fake%20AI-generated%20audio%20was%20superimposed%20on%20an%20old%20video%2C%20to%20make%20it%20look%20like%20the%20actor%20endorsed%20a%20political%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECLAIM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Aamir%20Khan%20endorsed%20the%20Congress'%20campaign%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFACT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20video%20dated%20back%20to%202014%2C%20which%20was%20digitally%20altered%20using%20an%20AI%20voice%20clone%20to%20make%20it%20look%20like%20the%20actor%20made%20a%20political%20endorsement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECONCLUSION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20social%20media%20users%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20Bollywood%20actor%20Aamir%20Khan%20in%20which%20he%20can%20be%20heard%20endorsing%20Congress%20party's%20campaign%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20while%20warning%20people%20against%20'jumlas'%20(catchphrases).%20In%20its%20investigation%2C%20the%20Desk%20found%20that%20a%2010-year-old%20video%20was%20digitally%20altered%20using%20AI%20voice%20clone%20to%20make%20it%20look%20like%20the%20actor%20made%20a%20political%20endorsement.%20The%20edited%20video%20was%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20with%20a%20false%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(This%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Ffact-detail%2FAnother-video-of-Aamir-Khan--with-superimposed-AI-generated-voice--shared-on-social-media-with-false-claim%2F1437066%5C%22%3EPTI%20Fact%20Check%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20republished%20by%20NDTV%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Shakti%20Collective.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713505440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fkffqudlo_aamir-khan_625x300_16_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-deepfake-of-aamir-khan-goes-viral-on-polling-day-heres-the-truth-5475066%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20social%20media%20users%20sh