orkspace%2C%20expand%20their%20book%20inventory%2C%20and%20bolster%20their%20marketing%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20new%20website%2C%20the%20duo%20are%20selling%20school%20books%20for%20ICSE%2C%20CBSE%20and%20Bihar%20Board%2C%20books%20for%20competitive%20exams%2C%20fiction%20and%20non-fiction%20books%2C%20along%20with%20new%20books.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20customers%20want%20new%20books%20and%20we%20are%20offering%20that%20at%20competitive%20prices%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Akshay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20are%20catering%20to%20almost%20200%20to%20250%20customers%20daily%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20claims%20Akshay.%20Their%20average%20order%20value%20is%20around%20Rs%201%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESameer%20Shrivastava%2C%20an%20engineering%20student%2C%20who%20bought%20a%20few%20books%20from%20Kitabwalah%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20rates%20are%20lesser%20than%20other%20sellers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20easy%20to%20access%20and%20offers%20a%20huge%20selection%20of%20books.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20ahead%2C%20Akshay%20wants%20Kitabwalah%20to%20become%20a%20one-stop%20shop%20for%20all%20things%20related%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341906%2Fwhere-to-donate-clothes-books-toys-anushka-jain-share-at-door-step-ngos-artificial-intelligence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebooks%20and%20school%20supplies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20our%20primary%20focus%20is%20on%20used%20books%2C%20we%20also%20want%20to%20sell%20stationery%2C%20school%20uniforms%2C%20e-books%2C%20audiobooks%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20the%20response%20of%20his%20family%20to%20their%20achievements%3F%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20incredibly%20proud.%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20first%20generation%20graduate%20and%20my%20family%20never%20imagined%20that%20I%20would%20start%20a%20business%20one%20day.%20It%E2%80%99s%20beyond%20our%20wildest%20dreams%2C