d%20to%20focus%20on%20people%20in%20these%20cities%20who%20are%20on%20the%20fringe%20of%20inclusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20sets%20Kinara%20Capital%20apart%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Kinara%20Capital%E2%80%99s%20launch%20in%202011%2C%20Hardika%20raised%20funds%20from%20social%20impact%20investment%20funds%20like%20Michael%20%26amp%3B%20Susan%20Dell%20Foundation%2C%20Patamar%20Capital%2C%20Gaja%20Capital%2C%20British%20International%20Investment%20(BII)%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kinara%20Capital%20runs%20HerVikas%20to%20help%20women%20entreprenuers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347265%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKinara%20Capital%20runs%20HerVikas%20to%20help%20women%20entreprenuers%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKinara%20vets%20its%20customers%20with%20the%20help%20of%20AI%20and%20Machine%20learning%2C%20with%20the%20last%20mile%20delivery%20done%20by%20its%20officers.%20They%20have%20133%20branches%20across%20100%20cities%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20have%20disbursed%20over%201%2C25%2C000%20loans%20so%20far%2C%20with%20assets%20under%20management%20of%20over%20Rs%203%2C170%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interest%20rates%20range%20from%2020%20to%2032%20percent%20on%20a%20reducing%20balance%20basis%2C%20with%20the%20average%20tenure%20ranging%20from%2036%20to%2038%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20underwriting%20is%2095%20percent%20digital%20and%205%20percent%20physical%2C%20through%20our%20sales%20officers%20on%20ground.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20blended%20tech%20model%20with%20a%20physical%20branch%20network%20where%20most%20of%20the%20underwriting%20and%20collections%20are%20done%20online%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20social%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%2020%20percent%20of%20their%20monthly%20disbursements%20go%20to%20existing%20customers%2C%20helping%20them%20grow%20their%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Kinara%E2%80%99s%20clients%2C%20Divya%20explains%20how%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20policy%20helped%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20runs%20a%20company%20called%20Brookwoods%20Technologies%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20take%20a%20loan%20for%20her%20business.%20Since%20her%20business%20was%20less%20than%20a%20year%20old%2C%20most%20lenders%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20NBFCs%20and%20banks%20lend%20after%20a%20business%20completes%20three%20years%20of%20operations.%20Kinara%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20such%20conditions%20and%20gave%20us%20a%20loan%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20immensely.%20The%20entire%20process%20was%20streamlined%20and%20online.%20An%20officer%20from%20their%20team%20came%20for%20inspection%20and%20sanctioned%20the%20loan%20very%20quickly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDivya%20has%20been%20able%20to%20grow%20her%20company%20to%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203%20crores%20in%203%20years.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20all%20this%2C%20Hardika%20states%20that%20Kinara%20is%20profitable%20today%20and%20rearing%20to%20reach%20more%20business%20owners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20Kinara%E2%80%99s%20existence%20began%20thanks%20to%20a%20woman%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20hence%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20their%20HerVikas%20programme%2C%20which%20offers%20discounts%20to%20women%20entrepreneurs%20to%20boost%20their%20businesses%2C%20remains%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20disbursed%20Rs%20700%20crores%20in%20the%20past%205%20years%2C%20offering%20a%201%20percent%20interest%20discount%2C%2060%20day%20repayment%20holiday%2C%2050%20reduction%20in%20processing%20fees.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%203.5%20percent%20to%204%20percent%20Non-Performing%20Asset%20(NPA)%20rate%2C%20Hardika%20wants%20to%20reach%20more%20MSMEs%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20hoping%20to%20reach%202%20lakh%20additional%20customers%20in%20the%20next%203%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20notion%20that%20unsecured%20business%20lending%20is%20risky%20and%20customers%20will%20disappear%20with%20your%20money.%20Our%20numbers%20prove%20that%20this%20is%20so%20far%20away%20from%20the%20truth.%20Customers%20are%20grateful%20to%20have%20access%20to%20capital%20and%20repay%20on%20time.%20They%20also%20use%20the%20money%20judiciously%20to%20grow%20their%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20enhance%20more%20jobs%20by%20reaching%20more%20small%20businesses.%20She%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20any%20business%20owner%20with%20potential%20to%20lose%20out%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20could%20have%20been%20a%20big%20franchise%20owner%20had%20Kinara%20been%20present%20then.%20Let%20no%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-har