e%20in%20demand%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201.85%20lakh%2C%20today%2C%20Anand%20reaps%20profits%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%207%20lakh%20on%20his%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%20More%20than%20the%20huge%20profits%2C%20the%2050-year-old%20finds%20contentment%20in%20leading%20a%20stress-free%20life%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20regret%20quitting%20my%20well-paying%20job.%20Earlier%2C%20I%20was%20a%20servant%20to%20a%20company%2C%20now%20I%20am%20a%20proud%20owner%20of%20a%20farm.%20I%20feel%20%3Cem%3Ethehrao%20%3C%2Fem%3E(composure)%20in%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Anand%20Mishra.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713166036000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347227%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Observing%20the%20year-round%20demand%20for%20lemons%2C%20Anand%20Mishra%20switched%20from%20growing%20traditional%20crops%20like%20wheat%2C%20paddy%2C%20and%20peas%20to%20cultivating%20lemons%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20With%20his%20two-acre%20farm%20now%20yielding%20Rs%207%20lakh%20in%20profits%2C%20he%20explains%20the%20reasoning%20behind%20this%20'unconventional'%20change.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347227%2Ffarmer-lemon-man-of-raebareli-uttar-pradesh-anand-mishra-earning-five-times-more-in-lakhs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20Pepper%2C%20Clove%2C%20Turmeric%20%26amp%3B%2015%20Types%20of%20Indian%20Spices%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELocated%20close%20to%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20Roorkee-based%20Dr%20Anshu%20Rathi%E2%80%99s%20kitchen%20smells%20heavenly.%20From%20cumin%E2%80%99s%20earthy%20aroma%20to%20refreshing%20fennel%20and%20